The Africa Food Show was recently launched by the global trade fair organiser and consultancy MIE Group through its Kenyan subsidiary GEX-MIE. This groundbreaking business-to-business (B2B) platform will be held on 24-26 June 2020 at the Kenyatta International Convention Centre (KICC). The event was attended by more than 10 country commercial attach√©s from the largest exporting markets to Kenya as well as key dignitaries from embassies.